'''大花三色堇'''（{{sn|''Viola'' ×''wittrockiana''}}）是[[堇菜科|堇菜科]][[堇菜屬|堇菜屬]]的一个園藝栽培种，由[[三色堇|三色堇]]与[[阿尔泰堇菜|阿尔泰堇菜]]、[[黄堇菜|黄堇菜]]杂交而得。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=''Viola''-studier II. Bidrag till de odlade penséernas historia med särskild hänsyn till deras härkomst|last=Wittrock|first=Veit Brecher|url=https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/86025#page/445/mode/1up|journal=Acta Horti Bergiani|issue=7|year=1895|volume=2|pages=5–6|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-date=2021-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502124300/https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/86025#page/445/mode/1up|dead-url=no}}</ref>大花三色堇誕生於1800年代的[[北歐|北歐]]，1820年代之後快速得到普及，成為主要園藝花卉之一。大花三色堇較為耐寒，主要在冬春開花。大花三色堇也是思想自由的象徵之一。

大花三色堇[[染色体|染色体]]数是2n = 44–52，<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Genetical and cytological investigations on ''Viola tricolor'' L. and ''V. arvensis'' Murr.|url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1111/j.1601-5223.1926.tb03159.x|last=Clausen|first=Jens Christian|date=1926|journal=Hereditas|issue=1-2|doi=10.1111/j.1601-5223.1926.tb03159.x|volume=8|pages=1–156|issn=1601-5223|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-date=2021-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210525174914/https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1111/j.1601-5223.1926.tb03159.x|dead-url=no}}</ref>通常为2n = 48。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Karyologic and heterosis studies of the artificial inter- and intraspecific hybrids of ''Viola'' ×''wittrockiana'' and ''Viola cornuta''|url=https://journals.ashs.org/hortsci/view/journals/hortsci/53/9/article-p1300.xml|last=Du|first=Xiaohua|last2=Wang|first2=Mengye|date=2018-09-01|journal=HortScience|issue=9|doi=10.21273/HORTSCI13098-18|volume=53|pages=1300–1305|language=en-US|issn=0018-5345|last3=Słomka|first3=Aneta|last4=Liu|first4=Huichao|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-date=2021-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210505025736/https://journals.ashs.org/hortsci/view/journals/hortsci/53/9/article-p1300.xml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

